  "response": "If someone is caught laundering money, they can face serious legal consequences, including:\n\n1. Criminal charges\n- Potential federal or state prosecution\n- Possible prison sentences\n- Substantial monetary fines\n\n2. Financial penalties\n- Seizure of assets involved in laundering\n- Mandatory financial restitution\n- Potential civil forfeiture\n\n3. Professional consequences\n- Loss of professional licenses\n- Difficulty obtaining future employment\n- Potential business/organizational sanctions\n\n4. Additional potential outcomes\n- Mandatory reporting to financial authorities\n- Inclusion on financial watchlists\n- Potential deportation for non-citizens\n\nThe specific penalties depend on the amount of money involved, jurisdiction, and individual circumstances of the case.",
